<div id="wrapper">
 <div id="main">
  <div class="inner_hotdeals">
  <%= render 'shared/header' %>
  <button onclick="topFunction()" id="myBtn" title="Go to top">Top</button>
  
   <div class="discount_show_wrapper">

     <div class="discount_show_image">
       <img src="<%= @code.discount_image %>">
       <p><%= @code.discount_source %></p>
     </div>

     <div class="discount_show_details">
       <h1 class="discount_title"><%= @code.discount_title %></h1>
       <p class="discount_name">Discount Code</p>
       <p class="discount_code"><%= @code.discount_code %></p>
       <p class="discount_date">End Date:<%= @code.discount_date %></p>
       <div class="discount_links">
        <a href="<%= @code.discount_link_01 %>">Use This Code</a>
        <a href="<%= @code.discount_link_02 %>">Use This Code In More Products</a>
       </div>
       <p class="discount_back"><%= link_to "See more codes >>", codes_path %></p>
       
       <div class="discount_offer">
        <h4>Special offers and product promotions</h4>

         <% if @code.discount_offer.present? %>
          <p><%= @code.discount_offer %></p>
         <% end %>
          <ul>
            <% if @code.discount_amazon_card.present? %>
             <li><a href="#">Get $50 off instantly: <%= @code.discount_amazon_card %></a> </li>
            <% end %>
            <% if @code.discount_used.present? %>
             <li>Buy Used and Save: <%= @code.discount_used %></br><a href="<%= @code.discount_used_link %>">See all Used offers.</a></li>
            <% end %>
            <% if @code.discount_coupon.present? %>
             <li><%= @code.discount_coupon %><a target="_blank" href="https://goo.gl/YEQwVD">(How to use)</a></br>
             <a href="https://amzn.to/2IyVx2r">See more "Coupons"</a></li>
            <% else %>
              <li><p class="no_code_coupon">There is no Coupon for <%= @code.discount_title %></p>
              <a href="/hotdeals/coupons">Find more "Coupons"</a></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
       </div>
     </div> 

     <div class="discount_show_random">
      <div class="discount_random">
       <%= link_to (image_tag @random_code.discount_image), code_path(@random_code) %>
       <h3><%= link_to @random_code.discount_title, code_path(@random_code) %></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="dicsount_ad">
        <a href="/search/quicksearch"><img src="https://i.pinimg.com/564x/e8/a6/ce/e8a6ced6c8256ce3664eac7261b0eb21.jpg"></a>
      </div>  
      <% if can? :update, @code %>
        <%= link_to "HOME", codes_path %>
        <%= link_to "Edit", edit_code_path(@code) %>
        <%= link_to "Delete", code_path(@code), method: :delete, data: { confirm: "Are you sure?" } %>
      <% end %>



   </div><!--/.discount_show_wrapper-->

 <h2>Title</h2>
  <div class="discount_grids">
    <% @random_shoes.each do |shoes| %>
     <div><%= link_to (image_tag shoes.main_img), shoes, { :class =>"random_images" } %></div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

 <h2>Title</h2>
 <div class="discount_grids">
  <% @random_gadgets.each do |gadget| %>
  <div class="random_images"><a href="/ecommerces/detail/<%= gadget.id %>"><img src="<%= gadget.image_main %>"></a></div>
  <% end %>
 </div>











 
   <% if @code.discount_amazon.present? %>
    <div class="discount_code_info">
      <div class="discount_amazon"><%= @code.discount_amazon %></div>
      <button class="discount_info_accordion">How do I use my Amazon promo code?</button>
      <div class="panel">
      <div class="how_to_use">
        <p>1.Copy your desired promotional code from the above list of active offers.</p>
        <p class="info_img"><img src="https://i.pinimg.com/564x/5b/cc/d3/5bccd338a30a25bdbb6b139ef2056aa2.jpg"><p>
        <p>2.Add the items you wish to order into your shopping cart by clicking Add to Cart. Ensure coupon conditions are met, including the types of items and the total price of your selected products.</p>
        <p class="info_img"><img src="https://i.pinimg.com/564x/5d/13/57/5d1357a4466ecdb98db05985b201a8f9.jpg"></p>
        <p>3.Click the Proceed to checkout button to continue with your order.</p>
        <p>4.Once you reach checkout, choose your shipping address and payment method.</p>
        <p class="info_img"><img src="https://i.pinimg.com/564x/f7/28/60/f72860dbcb9fde2267baf40c4e524c60.jpg"></p>
        <p>5.Enter the promotional code you wish to use and click Apply. The stated price reductions will then be applied to your checkout total.</p>
        <p class="info_img"><img src="https://i.pinimg.com/564x/b2/d1/55/b2d1559106d9a6c8ca77b56a476076b8.jpg"></p>
        <p>If you've encountered any of these issues, it means your code was used automatically.</p>
        <p class="info_img"><img src="https://i.pinimg.com/564x/59/6e/5c/596e5c63e52a5e512bdb4c17e8dc854f.jpg"></p>
        <p>You can check if your code was used or not on the Shipping & Payment page. OR</p>
        <p class="info_img"><img src="https://i.pinimg.com/564x/64/cd/cd/64cdcdb7de6e75c8116acde03a5ee4dd.jpg"></p>
        <p>You can check on the Place Orer page</p>
        <p>6.Then click Place your order.</p>
       </div>
      </div>

      <button class="discount_info_accordion">Why isn't my code working?</button>
      <div class="panel">
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</p>
      </div>
   </div>
  <% end %>





   
